<li><strong>AAG Harassment-Free Task Force </strong><a href="https://www.aag.org/aag-harassment-free-task-force-survey-report/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[SURVEY REPORT]</a></li>
<li><strong>Mental Health Task Force</strong> <a href="https://www.aag.org/mental-health-task-force-report/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[REPORT]</a></li>
